          <p>Stan Lemon is a software-focused technology leader who builds products that deliver real value to customers. He has led cross-functional teams, shipped software across platforms, and excels at bridging technical complexity with business goals so teams stay aligned and deliver results that matter. He lives in Indianapolis with his family, loves the Steelers, and built Dollar &amp; Sense for iOS, watchOS, and macOS to help his kids track chores and savings.</p>
